## Research Presentation {.centit}

::: {style="font-size: 2.1em; text-align: center"}
Maritime Security: Understanding the Causal Link Between Illegal Fishing And Maritime Piracy
:::

## Is illegal fishing related to maritime piracy?

-   Past works: illegal fishing and piracy correlated
-   **Foreign trawlers**--\>Deplete fishery--\>Local fishers turn to piracy (Ploch et al. 2011; Weir 2009; Desai and Shambaugh 2021)
-   But seemingly plausible, no such evidence (Denton and Harris 2021; Jesperson 2022)

