## Research Design {.smaller}

<br />

Presence of piracy in a grid-cell in a year? (Y-1/N-0 )

<br />

Independent variables:

-   IUU fishing in each grid-cell
-   Opportunity: Ship traffic

Control variable:

-   Night lights
-   Ports in each grid-cells
-   Security force bases in each grid-cell

